We collect information automatically when you use our Platform:
a. Usage details;
b. IP addresses;
c. Browser cookies;
d. Flash cookies;
e. Web beacons on our Website;
f. Web beacons in our emails;
g. Other tracking technologies.

We collect personal information from you in the following ways:
•
•
At registration on our Website, App, or Platform;
Through mobile and desktop applications your downloads from our Website, App, or
Platform;
a. When you interact with our advertising and applications on third-party websites and
services;
